	<item>
		<title>About</title>
		<link>http://localhost:1313/about/</link>
		<pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 16:46:38 +0100</pubDate>
		
		<guid>http://localhost:1313/about/</guid>
		<description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;about-me&#34;&gt;About Me&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;bio&#34;&gt;Bio&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;From Dublin etc&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m a recent graduate in Physics with Astronomy and Space Science from University College Dublin. I&amp;rsquo;m particularly interested in computing, and its applications to the field.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;research-interests&#34;&gt;Research Interests&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My research interests are&amp;hellip; maths and programming in space science.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;From September, I am starting a PhD with the Planetary Magnetospheres group at the Dublin Institute for Advanced Studies. I will be studying Mercury&amp;rsquo;s magnetosphere and its interaction with the solar environment through analysis of large data sets from the MESSENGER mission, and upon its arrival, BepiColombo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;hobbies&#34;&gt;Hobbies&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Outside of my research, I do lots of other hobbies! I love the outdoors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Whitewater and Sea kayaking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hiking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
	</item>
	
